<p>Cookies are small data files that can be placed on your hard drive by websites that you visit. The only personal information that a cookie can contain is information that you provide to us personally. CFH uses cookies to gather and store personal information that is collected when online transactions occur on our Website, as well as passwords and preferences.</p>
