<p>CFH will not rent, sell, lease, or share personal information about you with other organizations, except in response to subpoenas, court orders, or privacy processes, or to establish and/or exercise our legal rights. However, when an online donation occurs through our Website a third party merchant may be provided information in order to process the transaction.</p>
